China to Tighten Approval Process for Wind Power Projects, Securities Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-07T23:57:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/china-to-tighten-approval-process-for-wind-power-projects-securities-says.html
China  will tighten the approval
process for wind-power projects to slow the rapid growth of the
industry, China Securities Journal reported today, citing an
unidentified person.  Local governments must obtain approval from the National
Energy Administration for projects with installed capacity of
less than 50,000 kilowatts, the report said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  